Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.82,0:13:03.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她太快了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.81,0:13:33.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,休想…继续前进
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.29,0:13:38.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.46,0:14:06.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,萨提拉学姐用了分身
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.59,0:14:08.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 是加速吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.65,0:14:23.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,学姐 太厉害了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.36,0:14:24.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我应该说过
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.85,0:14:26.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用不着你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.46,0:14:34.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里是…什么地方
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.60,0:14:37.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说话了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.94,0:14:42.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…在干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.26,0:14:51.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道锁骨的圣痕
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.19,0:14:53.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正在支配她的意识
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.52,0:15:06.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下一招不打倒她的话 就撑不住了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.76,0:15:21.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和圣痕组织的一体化在加速
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.39,0:15:24.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样下去 学姐会…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.36,0:15:30.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无间隙双重加速
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.23,0:15:42.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又来了 像分身一样的…加速
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.91,0:15:56.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,三重加速
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.03,0:16:05.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,四重加速吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.97,0:16:17.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,追不上她的速度
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.95,0:16:40.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卡茜学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.48,0:16:43.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请恢复意识
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.67,0:16:44.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和也
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.82,0:16:51.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不是会做这种事的人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.58,0:16:53.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不是答应我了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.05,0:17:04.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希望有一天 能看到你的小说
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.32,0:17:08.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.63,0:17:33.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和也 快住手
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.00,0:17:36.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 不行
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.08,0:17:39.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说过的 用不着你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.08,0:17:43.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算萨提拉学姐不需要我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.95,0:17:48.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我 很需要学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.08,0:17:54.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为 为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.35,0:17:58.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为你 是我的拍档
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.19,0:18:00.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是姐姐她…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.57,0:18:04.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,继承了姐姐圣痕的 重要的人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.51,0:18:08.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟你一起 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.09,0:18:11.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我背后
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.95,0:18:13.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和也还活着
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.92,0:18:16.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 不只是你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.64,0:18:18.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有很多人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.42,0:18:20.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有很多珍贵事物
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.31,0:18:23.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想保护珍贵的人和物
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.64,0:18:41.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.51,0:18:44.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都在乱想什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.84,0:18:48.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和也根本没期望我当他姐姐的替身
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.51,0:18:50.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 说到底我这种人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.00,0:18:54.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么可能胜任潘多拉的英雄的替身
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.12,0:18:59.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对 和也想要的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.06,0:19:00.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是拍档
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.75,0:19:04.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了守护珍贵的人物的拍档
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.92,0:19:11.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我恨的 可能是移植到我身上的英痕
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.46,0:19:15.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我遇到了和也
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.08,0:19:18.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是没移植英痕
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.98,0:19:22.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我到现在都没拍档
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.62,0:19:31.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,遇到和也 是种幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.58,0:19:34.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要感谢青井和叶
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.69,0:19:36.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.16,0:19:38.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绝对不会输给任何人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.80,0:19:42.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,终有一天 连青井和叶也战胜
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.77,0:19:52.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和也 这场战斗结束后
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.30,0:19:53.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定要洗礼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.67,0:20:02.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和也
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.71,0:20:07.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,动不了 这次真的要完蛋了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.32,0:20:16.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明已经没有冰冻结界了 为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.71,0:20:18.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.43,0:20:22.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要逼我杀人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.74,0:20:25.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不想伤害任何人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.36,0:20:27.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有自己的梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.34,0:20:29.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从小就想
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.01,0:20:31.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当小说家
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.74,0:20:40.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,发生了什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.85,0:20:45.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托了 阻止我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.71,0:20:47.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,萨提莱莎·艾尔·布列吉特
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.63,0:20:53.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要被消灭了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.37,0:21:09.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伊莉莎白 发生了什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.00,0:21:29.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来 我打得太浅了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.85,0:21:46.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,敌方一名潘多拉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.75,0:21:50.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,入侵Ravensborne Nucleochede的“圣骸”安置室
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.36,0:23:31.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8} 之前一次都没…将这学园的人当过伙伴
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.45,0:23:28.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杀了我 已经…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.98,0:23:30.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,萨提莱莎…
